Subject: Still Interested in the [job_title] Role? Let's Connect!

Body:
<html><body style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#222222;font-size:14px;">
<p><strong>Hi [applicant_first_name],</strong></p>

<p>I hope you're doing well! We wanted to check in and see if you're still interested in the [job_title] role with Outsourced Pro Global.</p>

<p>Your application really stood out to us, and we believe your skills and experience are a great match for what we're looking for. We're excited about the possibility of you joining our team!</p>

<p>If you'd like to move forward, simply schedule an interview at a time that works best for you using the link below:</p>

<p><strong><a href="[Schedule Your Interview Here]">Schedule Your Interview Here</a></strong></p>

<p>Should you have any concerns or questions, please email, call, or text your Recruitment Specialist: [recruiter_phone_line]</p>

<p>Thank you for considering Outsourced Pro Global as your next career step. We look forward to connecting with you soon!</p>

[signature]
